{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PrybY8ikqRZQrezNXv4GYQ","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/400-challenge-engine/history.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ee923df0-ca95-4460-8036-5b0289591b86","uuid":"906f6c26-3f1e-4011-bce2-74026f805df8","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:00:11.166Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/400-challenge-engine/history.md","oldString":"---\n\n","newString":"---\n\n## Iteration 1 — Phase 0: Event types + game.settled emission (coinflip & lord)\n\n**Status**: Success\n\n**Changes**:\n- `backend/services/backend/src/queue/event-types.ts` — Added 5 new event types: `GAME_SETTLED`, `REWARD_POOL_FUND`, `POINTS_GRANT`, `CRATE_DROP`, `CRATE_SOL_PAYOUT`\n- `backend/services/backend/src/db.ts` — Added `rawSql` property to `Db` interface + implementation, so `emitEvent()` can be called within `withTransaction()` blocks\n- `backend/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts` — Emit `game.settled` event at the end of both `settleMatch()` (coinflip) and `settleLordRound()` (lord/jackpot) within the existing settlement DB transaction. Payload matches FR-1 schema: roundId, roundPda, game, players[] (with userId, wallet, amountLamports as string, isWinner, payoutLamports as string, isCreator), feeLamports as string, settledAt ISO 8601. Lord aggregates per-player totals (since a player can have multiple entries).\n- `backend/services/backend/src/__tests__/integration.test.ts` — Added 2 tests: (1) verifies game.settled event emitted with correct payload shape after coinflip settlement, (2) verifies duplicate settlement retry doesn't produce double events (phase guard rejects re-settle). Also added `event_queue`, `game_entries`, `transactions`, `player_profiles` to TRUNCATE list for test isolation.\n\n**Verification**: `cd backend && pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck && pnpm test` — all 124 tests pass (0 errors, 2 pre-existing warnings).\n\n","originalFile":"# Implementation History — 400-challenge-engine\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":6,"oldLines":3,"newStart":6,"newLines":15,"lines":[" "," ---"," ","+## Iteration 1 — Phase 0: Event types + game.settled emission (coinflip & lord)","+","+**Status**: Success","+","+**Changes**:","+- `backend/services/backend/src/queue/event-types.ts` — Added 5 new event types: `GAME_SETTLED`, `REWARD_POOL_FUND`, `POINTS_GRANT`, `CRATE_DROP`, `CRATE_SOL_PAYOUT`","+- `backend/services/backend/src/db.ts` — Added `rawSql` property to `Db` interface + implementation, so `emitEvent()` can be called within `withTransaction()` blocks","+- `backend/services/backend/src/worker/settle-tx.ts` — Emit `game.settled` event at the end of both `settleMatch()` (coinflip) and `settleLordRound()` (lord/jackpot) within the existing settlement DB transaction. Payload matches FR-1 schema: roundId, roundPda, game, players[] (with userId, wallet, amountLamports as string, isWinner, payoutLamports as string, isCreator), feeLamports as string, settledAt ISO 8601. Lord aggregates per-player totals (since a player can have multiple entries).","+- `backend/services/backend/src/__tests__/integration.test.ts` — Added 2 tests: (1) verifies game.settled event emitted with correct payload shape after coinflip settlement, (2) verifies duplicate settlement retry doesn't produce double events (phase guard rejects re-settle). Also added `event_queue`, `game_entries`, `transactions`, `player_profiles` to TRUNCATE list for test isolation.","+","+**Verification**: `cd backend && pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck && pnpm test` — all 124 tests pass (0 errors, 2 pre-existing warnings).","+"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
